==English==
===Noun===
'''apostilb'''

#{{physics}} a [[unit]] of [[luminance]], being the luminance of a perfectly [[diffusing]] [[surface]] [[emitting]] [[light]] at the rate of one [[lumen]] per [[square metre]].

